---
// FAQ Section Component
---

<section class="faq-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    
    <div class="faq-grid">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Do you require long-term contracts?</h3>
        <p>No. We work month-to-month because we believe in earning your business through results, not locking you into lengthy agreements.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How do you use AI in your marketing?</h3>
        <p>We use AI tools for competitor analysis, keyword research, content optimization, and campaign monitoring to deliver faster, more accurate results than traditional methods.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What makes you different from other Houston agencies?</h3>
        <p>Fresh perspective without the bureaucracy. You get direct access to decision makers, cutting-edge AI tools, competitive pricing, and personal attention your business deserves.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What's included in the free SEO audit?</h3>
        <p>Comprehensive analysis of your website's performance, competitor comparison, keyword opportunities, technical issues, and a clear action plan for improvement.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How quickly can you get started?</h3>
        <p>Most projects begin within 1-2 weeks. As a new agency, we have immediate availability and can move fast when you're ready to grow.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How do you keep me updated on progress?</h3>
        <p>Comprehensive monthly reports at the end of each month showing exactly what we've accomplished, metrics that matter, and next steps. No confusing jargon - just clear results you can understand.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* FAQ Section */
  .faq-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: #FAFAFA;
  }
  
  .faq-section .section-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  
  .faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    grid-template-rows: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .faq-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 1024px) and (min-width: 769px) {
    .faq-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      grid-template-rows: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
  
  .faq-item {
    background: transparent;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: left;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
  }
  
  .faq-item:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(249, 87, 56, 0.08), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95));
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(249, 87, 56, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(249, 87, 56, 0.2);
  }

  .faq-item h3 {
    color: #333;
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>